# this file describes magic powers available to magical order of Chess,
# which is of a highly mystical nature.
#
# the format for spirits is:
#	name level cost
# and for spells:
#	name level cost duration
#
# where `level' is the magical skill level at which you get the power,
# and `cost' is the cost in spell points to use the power.  `duration'
# tells how long a spell will last.
#
summon_pawn 40 1
summon_knight 90 4
summon_bishop 120 5
summon_rook 200 6
summon_queen 600 9
summon_king 1000 8
summon_master 1500 11
summon_grandmaster 2000 14
#
hide_sector 125 1 8
hide_army 200 1 2
mag_bonus 300 1 2
fly_army 400 2 2
water_walk 400 2 2
haste_army 600 3 2
#
castle 150 2 0
stalemate 500 1 4
